body:
Comment 6: 
Thanks for tracking down the source of the log prints.
I bet this is fixed.  The binaries used to map symbol table
and line number information a 0x99000000, which would
overlap with the 0x90000000+0x20000000 region shown
in the log message.  We don't do that anymore (as of the
last release), so I think this problem is probably gone.

@eric.bergstrome: can you please test and see if this
has fixed the problem for you?
